        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This suit of <em>+2 resilient chain mail</em> is made of fine white links of a strange and slightly translucent pale metal, and the sleeves and skirt are fashioned into smaller trails that resemble feathers. Unlike normal chain mail, <em>holy chain</em> has no Speed reduction, its armor check penalty is 0, and its Bulk is 1.</p>\n<p>You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC and saving throws against fiends. You appear radiant while you wear the armor, giving you a +2 item bonus to Diplomacy checks against all creatures except fiends.</p>\n<p>If you're unholy, you're @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} while wearing holy chain. You can't recover from this condition while wearing the armor.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activateâ€”Celestial Flight</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (concentrate)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The armor sprouts glowing wings that grant you a fly Speed of 30 feet. The wings shed bright light in a 40-foot radius (and dim light to the next 40 feet). The wings fade away after 10 minutes.</p><hr /><p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You're holy.</p>"
